.DT
new_mail
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
new_mail

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
new_mail -  This method returns a string saying if the player has new mail or not.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string new_mail(string pname)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^pname%^RESET%^ - the name of the player
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the new mail string
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/mailer.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns a string saying if the player has new mail or not.
This is what is used when the player first logs on.
.EP

.SH Example 1
.SI 5
str = MAIL_HANDLER->new_mail(TP->query_name());

.EI

